{"pageProps":{"article":{"id":"f72833bf80","title":"中央关于各省市区党委向中央汇报工作的补充通知","origin":"","is_range_date":false,"dates":[{"id":"0c439df895","index":0,"year":1956,"month":5,"day":20,"articleId":"f72833bf80"}],"tags":[{"id":"2d13338754","name":"指示","type":"文稿类型"},{"id":"994fc035d4","name":"工业战线","type":"主题/事件"},{"id":"dd2b275f6c","name":"毛泽东","type":"人物"}],"aliases":[],"publications":[{"id":"maoquanji36","name":"毛泽东全集第36卷","internal":false,"official":false,"type":"pdf","author":"张迪杰","files":"https://raw.githubusercontent.com/banned-historical-archives/banned-historical-archives0/main/mao-quanji/36-OCR.pdf"}],"authors":[{"id":"261e5467ec","name":"毛泽东"}]},"publication_details":{"maoquanji36":{"comments":[{"id":"97f82027a6","publicationId":"maoquanji36","articleId":"f72833bf80","index":1,"part_index":-99,"offset":-99,"text":"即中共中央1956年5月14日关于各省市区党委向中央汇报工作的具体安排的通知。"}],"contents":[{"id":"a088e76877","type":"title","text":"中央关于各省市区党委向中央汇报工作的补充通知","index":0,"publicationId":"maoquanji36","articleId":"f72833bf80"},{"id":"97f82027a6","type":"paragraph","text":"各省委，市委，自治区党委：","index":1,"publicationId":"maoquanji36","articleId":"f72833bf80"},{"id":"ae83639532","type":"paragraph","text":"最近广东、湖北、武汉、广州等省委市委向中央汇报财经工作，均是以当地整个财经工作为对象（包括中央各部管的和地方管的）；在工业方面多从中央各部管的大企业，例如长江大桥、武汉钢铁公司、长江航务局、广州造纸厂、广东糖业公司等总结经验；在财贸方面，也是以当地整个财政金融工作和贸易工作为对象，加以分析，提出意见。中央认为这样做是很好的。中央五月十四日电报中所说各地汇报对象可以地方管的或者希望由地方管的为主，而以中央各部管的为辅这一点规定，应予取消","index":2,"publicationId":"maoquanji36","articleId":"f72833bf80"},{"id":"fe07600a76","type":"subtitle","text":"中央","index":3,"publicationId":"maoquanji36","articleId":"f72833bf80"},{"id":"2df14a4080","type":"paragraph","text":"一九五六年五月二十日","index":4,"publicationId":"maoquanji36","articleId":"f72833bf80"}],"page":{"id":"341b513716","publicationId":"maoquanji36","articleId":"f72833bf80","start":365,"end":365}}}},"__N_SSG":true}